title: Seattle Snow, Client Therapists, Spoiled Children, and Parenting ADHD
description:
Dr. Kirk Honda and Rebecca Bloom talk about the Seattle snow storm,
clients who want to become therapists, how to spoiled children, and how to parent a child with ADHD.

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.

Feb 27, 2019.
